jects</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Unknown - moment of extraction (04/14)</span></p><p class=\"c4 c6\"><span class=\"c0\"></span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">362</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c8\"><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">UNFCCC Private Sector Initiative </span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c7\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fadaptation%2Fworkstreams%2Fnairobi_work_programme%2Fitems%2F6547.php&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNGdT_tLVBSAeTy9_6PB5_mb2mr_sg\">http://unfccc.int/adaptation/workstreams/nairobi_work_programme/items/6547.php</a></span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Private funded projects</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Unknown - moment of extraction (04/14)</span></p><p class=\"c4 c6\"><span class=\"c0\"></span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">101</span></p><p class=\"c4 c6\"><span class=\"c0\"></span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c8\"><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">ClimateWise</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c7\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.climatewise.org.uk%2F&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNHtdg98YT3ByDE0HKmDVl9ewaQN2w\">http://www.climatewise.org.uk/</a></span><sup><a href=\"#cmnt2\" name=\"cmnt_ref2\">[b]</a></sup></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Insurance funded projects</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c4 c6\"><span class=\"c0\"></span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">123</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c8\"><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c5 c6\"><span class=\"c0\">ClimateFundsUpdate</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c7\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.climatefundsupdate.org%2F&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNGSSUEBDaYI1eoxe4oBFHLMwGBIxA\">http://www.climatefundsupdate.org/</a></span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Projects funded by multi-lateral funds</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">2003-2013</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">312</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c8\"><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">OECD</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c7\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd.org%2Finvestment%2Fstats%2Fofficialdevelopmentassistancedefinitionandcoverage.htm&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNFgpLZz_2lh0I13WvPiidwj82RgfQ\">http://www.oecd.org/investment/stats/officialdevelopmentassistancedefinitionandcoverage.htm</a></span><span class=\"c0\">)</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Project funded by OECD countries through bilateral aid</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">2010-2012</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">3664</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c8\"><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">NAPAs (National Adaptation Programmes of Action)</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c7\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fadaptation%2Fworkstreams%2Fnational_adaptation_programmes_of_action%2Fitems%2F4583.php&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNFPh2K7RFFG410SLJ4QsNDPV1oGfQ\">http://unfccc.int/adaptation/workstreams/national_adaptation_programmes_of_action/items/4583.php</a></span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">Projects planned by Least Developed Countries</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span>Future priority projects list last updated </span><span>29 March 2012</span></p></td><td class=\"c3\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c6 c5\"><span class=\"c0\">498</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c5\"><span>ADD HERE THE TEXT BY ERIK ON HOW, WHERE AND WHEN THE DATA HAVE BEEN EXTRACTED AND TREATED</span><sup><a href=\"#cmnt3\" name=\"cmnt_ref3\">[c]</a></sup></p><p class=\"c4 c16\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c5\"><span>Each source uses different codes to classify climate risks. For consistency, all codes were, where possible, mapped on to the UNDP ALM sectors:</span></p><ul class=\"c9 lst-kix_291rhtmyd8re-0 start\"><li class=\"c1\"><span>agriculture / food security</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>coastal zone development</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>disaster risk reduction</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>health</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>infrastructure / risk management</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>natural resource management</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>rural development</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>water resources</span></li></ul><p class=\"c5\"><span>The UNDP ALM codes did not comprehensively cover all those included in the other sources and so three additional codes were included:</span></p><ul class=\"c9 lst-kix_vg31pxg2381b-0 start\"><li class=\"c1\"><span>education</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>government / trade / finance</span></li><li class=\"c1\"><span>other</span></li></ul><p class=\"c4 c13\"><span></span></p><h1 class=\"c5 c10\"><a name=\"h.xo94nwvaky1k\"></a><span>References</span></h1><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><p class=\"c4\"><span></span></p><div class=\"c11\"><p class=\"c6 c14\"><a href=\"#cmnt_ref1\" name=\"cmnt1\">[a]</a><span class=\"c0\">These are guesses. The value of each glyph will have to be decided on the basis of the actual values. </span></p><p class=\"c6 c14\"><span class=\"c0\">So please correct this before publishing!</span></p></div><div class=\"c11\"><p class=\"c6 c14\"><a href=\"#cmnt_ref2\" name=\"cmnt2\">[b]</a><span class=\"c0\">Couldn&#39;t find the database of projects</span></p></div><div class=\"c11\"><p class=\"c6 c14\"><a href=\"#cmnt_ref3\" name=\"cmnt3\">[c]</a><span class=\"c0\">Erik please add your text here</span></p></div>"
