      "<h1 class=\"c10\"><a name=\"h.z8f5pxp7ws2w\"></a><span>Authors</span></h1><p class=\"c13\"><span>Alexis Jacomy (m&eacute;dialab Sciences Po), David Laniado (Barcelona Media), Giovanni Magni (Density Design), Donato Ricci (m&eacute;dialab Sciences Po), Julie Simon (Young Foundation), Ashley Ball (Young Foundation), Erik Borra (DMI Amsterdam University), Marta Croce (Density Design), Romain Weikmans (Universit&eacute; Libre de Bruxelles), Alex Meunier (m&eacute;dialab Sciences Po), Michele Mauri (Density Design), Victoria Boelman (Young Foundation), Tommaso Venturini (m&eacute;dialab Sciences Po), Liliana Bounegru (DMI Amsterdam University), Federica Bardelli (Density Design), Hannah Kitcher (Young Foundation), Michael Rastall (Stockholm Environment Institute), Marina Bouchat (m&eacute;dialab Sciences Po),</span></p><p class=\"c4 c12\"><span></span></p><h1 class=\"c10\"><a name=\"h.d776skyws2fx\"></a><span>Data time-stamp</span></h1><p class=\"c4\"><span>The data for this map/tool have been originaly extracted in different sprints:</span></p><ul class=\"c19 lst-kix_8czwqdh0lhal-0 start\"><li class=\"c4 c7\"><span>UNDP adaptation learning mechanism - Oxford Sprint, 22-26 April 2014</span></li><li class=\"c4 c7\"><span>Ci-Grasp UNFCCC - Oxford Sprint, 22-26 April 2014</span></li><li class=\"c4 c7\"><span>Private Sector Initiative - Oxford Sprint, 22-26 April 2014</span></li><li class=\"c4 c7\"><span>ClimateWise - Oxford Sprint, 22-26 April 2014</span></li><li class=\"c4 c7\"><span>ClimateFundsUpdate - Paris Sprint, 6-10 January 2014</span></li><li class=\"c4 c7\"><span>OECD - Paris Sprint, 6-10 January 2014</span></li><li class=\"c13 c7\"><span>NAPAs (National Adaptation Programmes of Action) - Paris Sprint, 6-10 January 2014</span></li></ul><p class=\"c13\"><span>The map/tool has been developed during the Milan Sprint, 8-12 September 2014</span></p><h1 class=\"c10\"><a name=\"h.by2tmd68tmmy\"></a><span>Data source</span></h1><a href=\"#\" name=\"015eb90725ddc78c